      How do you add a picture to a project?
      Add an image to your project

      In Solution Explorer, open the shortcut menu for the project that you want to add the image to, and then choose Add > New Item. In the Add New Item dialog box, under Installed, select Graphics, and then select an appropriate file format for the image.      29-Apr-2022
